# OPTIONAL — only needed if you want a live "LIVE"/"HT" badge to appear
# faster than openfootball's once-daily sync. Without this, the app still
# works correctly and shows accurate final scores; matches just won't show
# a red LIVE badge while in progress.
# Get a free key (no credit card) at https://www.api-football.com/

API_FOOTBALL_KEY=

